{"tid":2009092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭北京施壓刪病毒起源字句　歐盟承認做法有錯","createTime":"2020-05-09T13:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T03:00:13.000Z","uid":30561,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"21e1f7ea488d6e6942fe9c4f73111b58e2d10475","tid":2009092,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:15:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=390432&amp;fbclid=IwAR0_-dWDQHejjajMysX_TEs3W2xclgn8OqcGeKn0s8qDzrv6yuu0OdY2u2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390432%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_-dWDQHejjajMysX_TEs3W2xclgn8OqcGeKn0s8qDzrv6yuu0OdY2u2w&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpXr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=778eba0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390432%26fbclid%3DIwAR0_-dWDQHejjajMysX_TEs3W2xclgn8OqcGeKn0s8qDzrv6yuu0OdY2u2w&h=a7a8a8b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=390432&amp;fbclid=IwAR0_-dWDQHejjajMysX_TEs3W2xclgn8OqcGeKn0s8qDzrv6yuu0OdY2u2w</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/c0.10.540.282a/p540x282/96782064_175129893749856_847157053318234112_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=eaa83b&amp;_nc_oc=AQk6E3xYT61tEPfES03k_z5YjR0OoABBsURqvtgpmAGeuCa8QhBJSVzHBHz5k1kBEvE&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=b9f04b7bebab439ce94c4c1bf98f6917&amp;oe=5EDC42BD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fc0.10.540.282a%2Fp540x282%2F96782064_175129893749856_847157053318234112_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_sid%3Deaa83b%26_nc_oc%3DAQk6E3xYT61tEPfES03k_z5YjR0OoABBsURqvtgpmAGeuCa8QhBJSVzHBHz5k1kBEvE%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Db9f04b7bebab439ce94c4c1bf98f6917%26oe%3D5EDC42BD&h=f9124ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】歐盟駐華代表團團長郁白聯同歐盟27國駐華大使，就歐中建交45周年發表文章。歐盟承認曾在中方施壓下作刪改，直認做法有錯。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟駐華代表團指，他們在《中國日報》及《人民日報》上發表的文章，原本提到新型冠狀病毒疫情在中國爆發，隨後在過去三個月傳播到世界其他地方，但遭到中方審查，《中國日報》最終刊登內容經刪減的文章，刪除了疫情起源和傳播部分，《人民日報》則沒有刊登。<br />\n<br />\n郁白說他原本不願意這樣做，但由於「時間緊迫」，在中方堅持下就範，對此表示遺憾。"},{"pid":"71a9c138cdc57cad2ccc885eb16210a8d2fe68e8","tid":2009092,"uid":108347,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"因為趕，所以含撚，會唔會係本身鍾意含撚呢"},{"pid":"f9cbfc86c6d44514f20cdb4eddfb2e6a6fcce765","tid":2009092,"uid":237465,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"咁肯將COVID-19 改返做 武漢肺炎未 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8442bc7025e25b1cadbc209f896fcf64dbc745","tid":2009092,"uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcS2_kw7waRVmcrYLM6_s7kL_3g79fqb6AlLQdi7fdL2KNteUD9h&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcS2_kw7waRVmcrYLM6_s7kL_3g79fqb6AlLQdi7fdL2KNteUD9h%26usqp%3DCAU&h=5f15fa9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b623297d06e8220860ed9d3eeae933cdd695d7","tid":2009092,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"冇人篤爆你又會認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79cfdea87b9d4b699a6f9d160ccdc316f4e57dd","tid":2009092,"uid":241612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71a9c138cdc57cad2ccc885eb16210a8d2fe68e8","tid":2009092,"uid":108347,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"因為趕，所以含撚，會唔會係本身鍾意含撚呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"含慣左<br />\n一時口快啫"},{"pid":"3deb5280a31c8e21e15c7cbaa22f70962dc87097","tid":2009092,"uid":34869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:05:27.000Z",